Ingredients
2 oz. London dry gin
1 oz. lemon juice
1 tsp. superfine sugar
1 egg white
club soda

How to Make it.
1. Shake ingredients (except club soda) furiously with cracked ice in a chilled cocktail shaker. 
Strain into a Collins glass and fill up with club soda. Serve with a stirring rod.

Dont have to have the egg white.. but it won't be as creamy
